<item>
            <title>[TIKA-1773] No XML Metadata output for JP2 files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-1773</link>
                <project id="12310631" key="TIKA">Tika</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;br/&gt;
Tika doesn&apos;t return output for JPEG2000 (.jp2) files in xhtml format. We&apos;re using tika libraries in our application and get only empty html output for this file type. If you open a jp2 file with the gui and switch to structured text view, you don&apos;t get any results. There is no exception.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
